% [2] Cunningham MO, Whittington MA, Bibbig A, Roopun A, LeBeau FEN, et al. (2004) A role for fast rhythmic bursting neurons in cortical gamma oscillations in vitro. Proc Natl Acad Sci USA 101:7152–7157.

